<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />Arise, Yahweh, in your anger;</para>

<para style="q1">stand up against the rage of my enemies;</para>

<para style="q1">wake up for my sake and carry out the righteous decrees that you have commanded for them.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />The countries are assembled all around you;</para>

<para style="q1">take once more your rightful place over them.</para>
